ation）中，纽约的黑人人口激增。<ref>{{Cite book |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=E_vRLcgEdGoC&pg=PR7#v=onepage&q&f=false |title=Harlem Renaissance Lives from the African American National Biography |last=Gates |first=Henry Louis |last2=Higginbotham |first2=Evelyn Brooks |date=2009 |publisher=Oxford University Press |isbn=9780195387957 |language=en |access-date=2019-10-04 |archive-date=2021-04-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210417164305/https://books.google.com/books?id=E_vRLcgEdGoC&pg=PR7#v=onepage&q&f=false |dead-url=no }}</ref>

