根据2010年人口普查，纽约市的亚裔人口超过100万，多于旧金山和洛杉矶的总和<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2011/06/24/nyregion/asian-new-yorkers-asian-new-yorkers-seek-power-to-match-surging-numbers.html |title=Asian New Yorkers Seek Power to Match Numbers |author=Kirk Semple |date=2011-06-23 |work=[[纽约时报|The New York Times]] |accessdate=2011-07-05 |quote=Asians, a group more commonly associated with the West Coast, are surging in New York, where they have long been eclipsed in the city's kaleidoscopic racial and ethnic mix. For the first time, according to census figures released in the spring, their numbers have topped one million—nearly 1 in 8 New Yorkers—which is more than the Asian population in the cities of San Francisco and Los Angeles combined. |archive-date=2021-04-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210417164450/https://www.nytimes.com/2011/06/24/nyregion/asian-new-yorkers-asian-new-yorkers-seek-power-to-match-surging-numbers.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，市区的亚裔人口为全美最多<ref>{{Cite web |title=Asian American Statistics |url=http://www.ameredia.com/resources/demographics/asian_american.html |accessdate=2011-07-05 |publisher=Améredia Incorporated |archive-date=2011-07-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110714063833/http://www.ameredia.com/resources/demographics/asian_american.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2010年，纽约6.0%的人口为[[华裔美国人|华裔]]，其中40%居住于皇后区；[[韩裔美国人|韩裔]]占到1.2%，[[日裔美国人|日裔]]占0.3%；[[菲律賓裔美國人|菲裔]]为东南亚族群最多，占0.8%，其次为[[越裔美国人|越裔]]，占0.2%；[[印度裔美国人|印度裔]]为南亚族群最多，占2.4%，随后是孟加拉裔和巴基斯坦裔，各占0.7%和0.5%<ref>{{Cite web |title=Table SF1-P9 NYC: Total Asian Population by Selected Subgroups |url=http://www.nyc.gov/html/dcp/pdf/census/census2010/t_sf1_p9_nyc.pdf |accessdate=2011-08-27 |publisher=NYC.gov |archive-date=2012-05-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120505180239/http://www.nyc.gov/html/dcp/pdf/census/census2010/t_sf1_p9_nyc.pdf |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

由于总人口庞大，纽约的欧裔（非拉丁裔）白人人口亦是在全美各大城市（市区）中最多，2012年达到270万，超过洛杉矶（110万）、芝加哥（86.5万）和休斯顿（55万）白人人口的总和<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://factfinder2.census.gov/faces/tableservices/jsf/pages/productview.xhtml?pid=ACS_12_1YR_DP05&prodType=table |title=American FactFinder - Results<!-- Bot generated title --> |access-date=2014-01-25 |archive-date=2014-10-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006074901/http://factfinder2.census.gov/faces/tableservices/jsf/pages/productview.xhtml?pid=ACS_12_1YR_DP05&prodType=table |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[欧裔美国人|欧裔美国人]]人口非常多样化，根据12年统计局估计，[[意大利裔美国人|意大利裔]]人口达560,000人，[[爱尔兰裔美国人|爱尔兰裔]]385,000人，[[德裔美国人|德裔]]253,000人，[[俄裔美国人|俄裔]]223,000人，[[波兰裔美国人|波兰裔]]201,000人，{{Link-en|英裔美国人|English American|英裔}}137,000人，[[希腊裔美国人|希腊裔]]和[[法裔美国人|法裔]]各约65,000人，[[匈牙利裔美国人|匈牙利裔]]60,000人，[[乌克兰裔美国人|乌克兰裔]]55,000人，[[苏格兰裔美国人|苏格兰裔]]35,000人，{{Link-en|挪威裔美国人|Norwegian American|挪威裔}}和{{Link-en|瑞典裔美国人|Swedish American|瑞典裔}}各20,000人。此外，{{Link-en|捷克裔美国人|Czech American|捷克裔}}、[[立陶宛裔美国人|立陶宛裔]]、[[葡萄牙裔美国人|葡萄牙裔]]、[[苏格兰-爱尔兰裔美国人|苏格兰-爱尔兰裔]]和{{Link-en|威尔士裔美国人|Welsh American|威尔士裔}}各有12,000至14,000人不等<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://factfinder2.census.gov/faces/tableservices/jsf/pages/productview.xhtml?pid=ACS_12_1YR_DP02&prodType=table |title=American FactFinder - Results<!-- Bot generated title --> |access-date=2014-01-27 |archive-date=2014-12-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141211041932/http://factfinder2.census.gov/faces/tableservices/jsf/pages/productview.xhtml?pid=ACS_12_1YR_DP02&prodType=table |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

