008-07-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080704170220/http://losangeles.dodgers.mlb.com/la/history/timeline01.jsp |dead-url=no }}</ref>和5次夺冠，后来两支球队都于1958年迁往加利福尼亚<ref>{{Cite web |title=Historical Moments |url=http://www.dodgers-giants.com/ |accessdate=2012-05-31 |publisher=Dodgers Giants |archive-date=2012-07-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120715022539/http://www.dodgers-giants.com/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。此外纽约还有两支[[美国职棒小联盟|美国职棒小联盟]]球队，分别是{{Link-en|布鲁克林旋风|Brooklyn Cyclones}}队<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20120530&content_id=32491896&vkey=pr_mlb&c_id=mlb |title=Major League Baseball, Police Athletic League and the Brooklyn Cyclones to host free MLB Umpire Camp |date=2012-05-30 |newspaper=MLB Press Release |accessdate=2012-05-31 |archive-date=2013-01-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130131065126/http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20120530&content_id=32491896&vkey=pr_mlb&c_id=mlb |dead-url=no }}</ref>和{{Link-en|斯塔滕岛洋基|Staten Island Yankees}}队<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.silive.com/siyankees/index.ssf/2012/05/new_ownership_group_for_staten.html |title=New ownership group for Staten Island Yankees talks about future plans |date=2012-05-31 |newspaper=Silive |accessdate=2012-05-17 |archive-date=2012-05-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120527172514/http://www.silive.com/siyankees/index.ssf/2012/05/new_ownership_group_for_staten.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

