== 教育 ==
{{Main|纽约市教育}}
[[File:Butler_Library_-_1000px_-_AC.jpg|缩略图]]巴特勒圖書館]]
[[File:NYU's_Bobst_library-2.jpg|缩略图]]圖書館]]
纽约市的公立学校体系由[[纽约市教育局|纽约市教育局]]管理，为全美最大<ref>{{Cite journal |title=New York City Department of Education - About Us |url=http://schools.nyc.gov/AboutUs/default.htm |publisher=NYC Department of Education |accessdate=2012-05-31 |year=2012 |postscript=<!--None--> |journal= |archive-date=2007-09-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070905071308/http://schools.nyc.gov/AboutUs/default.htm |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，近110万名学生分别在超过1,200所中小学校就读<ref>{{Cite web |title=School Enrollment by Level of School and Type of School for Population 3 Years and Over |url=http://home2.nyc.gov/html/dcp/download/census/sf3edp302.xls |accessdate=2008-09-01 |year=2000 |format=MS Excel |publisher={{tsl|en|New York City Department of City Planning||New York City Department of City Planning}} |archive-date=2010-06-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100603080909/http://home2.nyc.gov/html/dcp/download/census/sf3edp302.xls |dead-url=no }}</ref>。此外市内还有近900所私立世俗和教会学校<ref>{{Cite web |title=Private School Universe Survey |url=http://nces.ed.gov/surveys/pss/ |accessdate=2008-09-01 |publisher=National Center for Education Statistics |archive-date=2008-09-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080906170332/http://www.nces.ed.gov/surveys/pss/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在2000年纽约市人口普查中，近594,000名学生参加了[[高等教育|高等教育]]，这一数字在全美最高<ref>{{Cite journal |title=New York in Focus: A Profile from Census 2000 |url=http://www.brookings.edu/es/urban/livingcities/newyork2.pdf |date=November 2003 |publisher=Brookings Institution |accessdate=2008-09-01 |format=PDF |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20061121164151/http://www.brookings.edu/es/urban/livingcities/newyork2.pdf |archivedate=2006-11-21 |deadurl=yes}}</ref>。2005年，每5个曼哈顿居民中就有3个是大学毕业生，每4个中就有1个有高等学位，这也是全美高教育水平者最为集中的区域<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=9404E7DE143EF935A2575BC0A9609C8B63 |title=New York Area Is a Magnet For Graduates |author=McGeehan, Patrick |date=2006-08-16 |work=The New York Times |accessdate=2007-03-27 |archive-date=2018-02-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180203162521/https://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=9404E7DE143EF935A2575BC0A9609C8B63 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

纽约还是许多知名私立大学的所在地，其中包括[[巴纳德学院|巴纳德学院]]、[[哥伦比亚大学|哥伦比亚大学]]、[[库伯联盟学院|库伯联盟学院]]、[[福坦莫大学|福坦莫大学]]、[[纽约大学|纽约大学]]、[[纽约科技学院|纽约科技学院]]、[[佩斯大学|佩斯大学]]和[[叶史瓦大学|叶史瓦大学]]等。公立[[纽约市立大学|纽约市立大学]]系统是全美最大的大学系统之一，其中包括许多本科学院和[[社区学院|社区学院]]。此外纽约还有一些规模较小的私立学院和大学，其中包括宗教学校和专业学校，例如[[圣若望大学|圣若望大学]]、[[朱利亚德学院|朱利亚德学院]]、[[曼哈顿学院|曼哈顿学院]]、{{Link-en|蒙特圣文森学院|College of Mount Saint Vincent}}、[[新学院|新学院]]、[[普瑞特艺术学院|普瑞特学院]]、[[视觉艺术学院_(纽约)|视觉艺术学院]]和[[瓦格纳学院|瓦格纳学院]]。
[[File:Fordham_University_14.JPG|右]]圖書館]]

纽约的科学研究主要集中在医学和生命科学领域。纽约在授予生命科学研究生学位的数量上排名全美第一，为40,000名持照医师和127位[[诺贝尔奖得主列表|诺贝尔奖得主]]提供教育背景<ref name="NYC science institutions">{{Cite press release |title=Mayor Michael R. Bloomberg and Economic Development Corporation President Andrew M. Alper Unveil Plans to Develop Commercial Bioscience Center in Manhattan |publisher=New York City Economic Development Corporation |url=http://home2.nyc.gov/portal/site/nycgov/menuitem.c0935b9a57bb4ef3daf2f1c701c789a0/index.jsp?pageID=mayor_press_release&catID=1194&doc_name=http%3A%2F%2Fhome2.nyc.gov%2Fhtml%2Fom%2Fhtml%2F2004b%2Fpr310-04.html&cc=unused1978&rc=1194&ndi=1 |date=2004-11-18 |accessdate=2008-09-01 |archive-date=2007-10-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071011233830/http://home2.nyc.gov/portal/site/nycgov/menuitem.c0935b9a57bb4ef3daf2f1c701c789a0/index.jsp?pageID=mayor_press_release&catID=1194&doc_name=http%3A%2F%2Fhome2.nyc.gov%2Fhtml%2Fom%2Fhtml%2F2004b%2Fpr310-04.html&cc=unused1978&rc=1194&ndi=1 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。在所有美国城市中，纽约从[[国立卫生研究院_(美国)|国立卫生研究院]]获得的年度资金数目居第二<ref>{{Cite web |title=NIH Domestic Institutions Awards Ranked by City, Fiscal Year 2003 |url=http://report.nih.gov/award/trends/top100fy03.htm |accessdate=2007-03-26 |year=2003 |publisher=National Institutes of Health |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090626092327/http://report.nih.gov/award/trends/top100fy03.htm |archivedate=2009-06-26 |deadurl=yes}}</ref>。主要的生物医学研究机构包括{{Link-en|纪念斯隆-凯特林癌症中心|Memorial Sloan–Kettering Cancer Center}}、[[洛克菲勒大学|洛克菲勒大学]]、{{Link-en|纽约州立大学州南部医学中心|SUNY Downstate Medical Center}}、[[阿尔伯特·爱因斯坦医学院|阿尔伯特·爱因斯坦医学院]]、[[西奈山医学院|西奈山医学院]]和{{Link-en|威尔·康奈尔医学院|Weill Cornell Medical College}}。2011年12月19日，纽约市市长迈克尔·布隆伯格宣布允许[[康奈尔大学|康奈尔大学]]和[[以色列理工学院|以色列理工学院]]斥资20亿美元于[[罗斯福岛_(纽约)|罗斯福岛]]上建设[[应用科学|应用科学]]研究生院，旨在将纽约转变为世界的科技首都<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2011/12/20/nyregion/cornell-and-technion-israel-chosen-to-build-science-school-in-new-york-city.html?scp=3&sq=cornell&st=cse |title=Cornell Alumnus Is Behind $350 Million Gift to Build Science School in City |author=RICHARD PéREZ-PE?A |date=2011-12-19 |publisher=The New York Times |accessdate=2011-12-20 |archive-date=2021-04-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210417165426/https://www.nytimes.com/2011/12/20/nyregion/cornell-and-technion-israel-chosen-to-build-science-school-in-new-york-city.html?scp=3&sq=cornell&st=cse |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |title='Game-changing' Tech Campus Goes to Cornell, Technion |url=http://www.news.cornell.edu/stories/Dec11/NYCcover.html |accessdate=2011-12-20 |date=2011-12-19 |last=Ju |first=Anne |publisher=Cornell University |archive-date=2012-10-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121028035316/http://www.news.cornell.edu/stories/Dec11/NYCcover.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

[[纽约公共图书馆|纽约公共图书馆]]为全美藏书量最大的图书馆系统，服务于曼哈顿、布朗克斯和史泰登島<ref name="libraryspot">{{Cite web |title=Nation's Largest Libraries |url=http://www.libraryspot.com/lists/listlargestlibs.htm |accessdate=2008-09-01 |publisher=LibrarySpot |archive-date=2007-05-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070529215517/http://www.libraryspot.com/lists/listlargestlibs.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。下属数家科研图书馆，包括{{Link-en|尚博格黑人文化研究中心|Schomburg Center for Research in Black Culture}}。[[皇后图书馆|皇后公共图书馆]]服务于皇后区，是全美第二大图书馆系统。[[布鲁克林公共图书馆|布鲁克林公共图书馆]]服务于布鲁克林<ref name="libraryspot" />。

