纽约市是全球商业和经贸的枢纽，与伦敦和东京并列为世界上三个最重要的[[金融|金融]]中心<ref>{{Cite book |title=The Global City: New York, London, Tokyo |last=Sassen, Saskia |authorlink=Saskia Sassen |publisher=Princeton University Press |year=2001 |isbn=0-691-07063-6 |edition=2nd}}</ref>，此外还是全美的银行业、零售业、世界贸易、运输、旅游业、地产业、[[新媒体|新媒体]]、传统媒体、广告业、法律服务、会计业、保险业、戏剧、时尚和艺术产业的中心。

根据2010年的数据，纽约都会区的都会生产总值（GMP，与国内生产总值概念类似）达到近1.28万亿美元<ref>{{Cite web |title=Gross Metropolitan Product |url=http://greyhill.com/gross-metropolitan-product |accessdate=2011-10-06 |publisher=Greyhill Advisors |archive-date=2011-11-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111106073959/http://greyhill.com/gross-metropolitan-product/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，是美国最大的区域经济体。2008年年底，纽约掌控了全球40%的金融资金，使之成为全球最大的金融中心<ref name="London vs. New York">{{Cite web |title=London vs. New York, 2005–06 |url=http://www.cincodias.com/articulo/mercados/Londres-versus-Nueva-York/20080901cdscdimer_3/cdsmer/ |accessdate=2008-03-11 |format=PDF |publisher=Cinco Dias |archive-date=2011-08-21 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/616yQKWnF?url=http://www.cincodias.com/articulo/mercados/londres-versus-nueva-york/20080901cdscdimer_3/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="New York still World">{{Cite web |title=London may have the IPOs ... |url=http://www.marketwatch.com/story/credit-crunch-shows-new-york-is-still-worlds-financial-capital/ |accessdate=2009-08-30 |publisher=Marketwatch |archive-date=2011-08-21 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/616yRlAPk?url=http://www.marketwatch.com/story/credit-crunch-shows-new-york-is-still-worlds-financial-capital/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Is New York still the World">{{Cite news |url=http://freakonomics.blogs.nytimes.com/2008/02/07/is-new-york-still-the-financial-capital-of-the-world/ |title=Is New York Still the Financial Capital of the World? |last=Dubner |first=Stephen J. |date=2008-02-07 |work=New York Times |accessdate=2009-08-30 |archive-date=2009-05-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090531212005/http://freakonomics.blogs.nytimes.com/2008/02/07/is-new-york-still-the-financial-capital-of-the-world/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。
[[File:Photos_NewYork1_032.jpg|缩略图]]的[[纽约证券交易所|纽约证券交易所]]是世界上上市公司总[[市值|市值]]最大的证券交易所<ref>{{Cite web |title=Market highlights for first half-year 2010 |url=http://www.world-exchanges.org/files/file/stats%20and%20charts/July%202010%20WFE%20Market%20Highlights.pdf |accessdate=2011-05-01 |publisher=World Federation of Exchanges |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130722235155/http://www.world-exchanges.org/files/file/stats%20and%20charts/July%202010%20WFE%20Market%20Highlights.pdf |archivedate=2013-07-22 |deadurl=yes}}</ref>]]

在针对120座城市的研究调查中，纽约在吸引[[资本|资本]]、商业和游客的能力上排名第一<ref>{{Cite web |title=New York City Tops Global Competitiveness, Economist Report Says |url=http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-12/new-york-city-tops-global-competitiveness-london-is-no-2-economist-says.html |accessdate=2012-03-13 |author=Michelle Kaske |date=2012-03-12 |publisher=Bloomberg L.P. |archive-date=2012-03-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120312173905/http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-12/new-york-city-tops-global-competitiveness-london-is-no-2-economist-says.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2012年7月，[[英国|英国]][[曼切斯特联足球俱乐部|曼切斯特联足球俱乐部]]宣布将在[[纽约证券交易所|纽约证券交易所]]进行[[首次公开募股|首次公开募股]]<ref>{{Cite web |title=Manchester United picks NYSE for U.S. public offering |url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2012/07/04/us-manchesterunited-ipo-idUSBRE86219520120704 |accessdate=2012-07-04 |author=Sharanya Hrishikesh and Ashutosh Pandey |date=2012-07-03 |publisher=Thomson Reuters |archive-date=2013-10-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131015020037/http://www.reuters.com/article/2012/07/04/us-manchesterunited-ipo-idUSBRE86219520120704 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

许多大型企业都在纽约市设立总部，财富美国500强中就有45家公司的总部位于该市<ref>[http://money.cnn.com/magazines/fortune/fortune500/2011/cities/ ''Fortune'' 500 web site (cities)] {{Wayback|url=http://money.cnn.com/magazines/fortune/fortune500/2011/cities/ |date=20110824184919 }}, retrieved July 21, 2011; ''Fortune'', Vol. 163, no. 7 (May 23, 2011), page F-45</ref>。同其他美国大城市相比，纽约还有较高比例的外国公司，平均每十个就业岗位中就有一个来自外国公司<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.gothamgazette.com/article/fea/20060123/202/1727 |title=Keeping the Economy Growing |author=Wylde, Kathryn |date=2006-01-23 |publisher=Gotham Gazette |accessdate=2008-09-01 |archive-date=2008-10-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081006220133/http://www.gothamgazette.com/article/fea/20060123/202/1727 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。强大的吸引外资的能力使纽约在《{{Link-en|FDi杂志|FDi Magazine}}》2013年的“美国未来城市”榜单中排列首位<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.fdiintelligence.com/Locations/Americas/American-Cities-of-the-Future-2013-14 |title=American Cities of the Future 2013-14 |author=Walls, Jacqueline |date=2013-04-08 |publisher=fDiIntelligence.com |accessdate=2013-08-05 |archive-date=2013-07-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130723035752/http://www.fdiintelligence.com/Locations/Americas/American-Cities-of-the-Future-2013-14 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

房地产是纽约市经济成长的重要动力。2015[[财政年度|财年]]纽约全市的地产总值估计为9,148亿美元<ref name="NYC real estate">{{Cite web |title=DEPARTMENT OF FINANCE PUBLISHES FISCAL YEAR 2015 TENTATIVE ASSESSMENT ROLL |url=http://www.nyc.gov/html/dof/downloads/pdf/press_release/fy2015_ta_roll_press_release.pdf |accessdate=2014-01-23 |date=2014-01-15 |publisher=New York City Department of Finance |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140202200729/http://www.nyc.gov/html/dof/downloads/pdf/press_release/fy2015_ta_roll_press_release.pdf |archivedate=2014-02-02 |deadurl=yes}}</ref>，其中[[时代华纳中心|时代华纳中心]]的估值最高，在2006年达到11亿美元<ref name="NYC real estate" />。纽约同时还是全国乃至全世界最有价值的一些地产的所在地。2007年7月2日，[[公园大道|公园大道]]450号以5.1亿美元的价值售出，每平方英尺价值约为1,589美元（17,104美元/平方米），打破了一个月前（2007年6月）由麦迪逊大道660号创造的每平方英尺1,476美元（15,887美元/平方米）的办公楼地产记录<ref>Quirk, James. {{Cite web |title=Bergen offices have plenty of space |url=http://www.northjersey.com/page.php?qstr=eXJpcnk3ZjczN2Y3dnFlZUVFeXk4NDImZmdiZWw3Zjd2cWVlRUV5eTcxNjI5NzEmeXJpcnk3ZjcxN2Y3dnFlZUVFeXkyMg== |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071222235142/http://www.northjersey.com/page.php?qstr=eXJpcnk3ZjczN2Y3dnFlZUVFeXk4NDImZmdiZWw3Zjd2cWVlRUV5eTcxNjI5NzEmeXJpcnk3ZjcxN2Y3dnFlZUVFeXkyMg== |archivedate=2007-12-22 |deadurl=yes}}, ''{{tsl|en|The Record (Bergen County)||The Record (Bergen County)}}'', July 5, 2007. Accessed July 5, 2007. "On Monday, a 26-year-old, 33-story office building at 450 Park Ave. sold for a stunning $1,589 per square foot, or about ,10 million. The price is believed to be the most ever paid for a U.S. office building on a per-square-foot basis. That broke the previous record—set four weeks earlier—when 660 Madison Ave. sold for $1,476 a square foot."</ref>。

纽约的电影与电视产业为全美第二大，仅次于[[好莱坞|好莱坞]]<ref>{{Cite web |title=NYC Film Statistics |url=http://www.nyc.gov/html/film/html/news/stats.shtml |accessdate=2008-09-01 |publisher=Mayor's Office of Film, Theatre, and Broadcasting |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080214051145/http://www.nyc.gov/html/film/html/news/stats.shtml |archivedate=2008-02-14 |deadurl=yes}}</ref>。新媒体、广告、时尚、设计和建筑等创意产业的就业机会与日俱增，竞争力也相当强大<ref>{{Cite journal |title=New York as a Global Creative Hub: A Competitive Analysis of Four Theories on World Cities |url=https://archive.org/details/sim_economic-development-quarterly_2006-11_20_4/page/330 |author=Currid, Elizabeth |journal=Economic Development Quarterly |issue=4 |doi=10.1177/0891242406292708 |year=2006 |volume=20 |pages=330–350}}</ref>。

纽约是多条{{Link-en|跨大西洋通讯电缆|Transatlantic communications cable|跨大西洋光纤缆线}}的终点，由此促进了[[生物科技|生物科技]]、[[软件开发|软件开发]]、[[游戏设计|游戏设计]]和网络服务等高科技产业的成长<ref>{{Cite web |title=Telecommunications and Economic Development in New York City: A Plan for Action |url=http://www.nycedc.com/about_us/TelecomPlanMarch2005.pdf |accessdate=2006-07-19 |date=March 2005 |format=PDF |publisher=New York City Economic Development Corporation |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080307231248/http://www.nycedc.com/about_us/TelecomPlanMarch2005.pdf |archivedate=2008-03-07 |deadurl=yes}}</ref>。其他重要的经济领域包括医疗研究与科技、[[非营利组织|非营利组织]]和大学。制造业在就业方面比例也很高，但近年在呈下降态势，其主要产品包括服饰、化工产品、金属制品、加工食品和家具等<ref>{{Cite web |title=Protecting and Growing New York City's Industrial Job Base |url=http://www.nyc.gov/html/imb/downloads/pdf/whitepaper.pdf |accessdate=2008-09-01 |date=January 2005 |format=PDF |publisher=The Mayor's Office for Industrial and Manufacturing Business |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111016072613/http://www.nyc.gov/html/imb/downloads/pdf/whitepaper.pdf |archivedate=2011-10-16 |deadurl=yes}}</ref>。其中，食品加工业是纽约最为稳定的制造行业<ref name="food manufacturing">{{Cite web |title=More Than a Link in the Food Chain |url=http://www.nyc.gov/html/imb/downloads/pdf/more_than_link_food_chain.pdf |accessdate=2008-09-01 |date=February 2007 |format=PDF |publisher=The Mayor's Office for Industrial and Manufacturing Business |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080831013513/http://www.nyc.gov/html/imb/downloads/pdf/more_than_link_food_chain.pdf |archivedate=2008-08-31 |deadurl=yes}}</ref>，产业价值达到50亿美元，员工数超过19,000人，巧克力是最主要的出口特产，年出口额达2.34亿美元<ref name="food manufacturing" />。

=== 华尔街 ===
{{main|华尔街}}

2013年，[[曼哈顿|曼哈顿]]的办公面积达到近52,000万平方英尺（5.2亿平方英尺，约4,810万平方米）<ref>{{Cite web |title=What is an office condominium? |url=http://www.rudderpg.com/faqs/ |accessdate=2013-05-28 |publisher=Rudder Property Group |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100929171315/http://www.rudderpg.com/faqs/ |archivedate=2010-09-29 |deadurl=yes}}</ref>，在办公市场上排名全美第一<ref>{{Cite web |title=Understanding The Manhattan Office Space Market |url=http://www.officespaceseeker.com/manhattan-office-space-market.html |accessdate=2013-05-18 |publisher=Officespaceseeker.com |archive-date=2014-07-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140713071533/http://www.officespaceseeker.com/manhattan-office-space-market.html |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。[[曼哈顿中城|曼哈顿中城]]是全美最大的[[中心商务区|中心商务区]]<ref>{{Cite web |title=Marketbeat United States CBD Office Report 2Q11 |url=http://www.cushwake.com/cwmbs2q11/PDF/off_us_cbd_2q11.pdf |accessdate=2015-05-02 |publisher=Cushman & Wakefield, Inc |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130508231043/http://www.cushwake.com/cwmbs2q11/PDF/off_us_cbd_2q11.pdf |archivedate=2013-05-08 |deadurl=yes}}</ref>。

[[曼哈顿下城|曼哈顿下城]]是全美第三大的中心商务区，其中世界上第一和第二大的证券交易所（按日均交易量和总[[市值|市值]]）——位于华尔街的[[纽约证券交易所|纽约证券交易所]]和[[纳斯达克|纳斯达克]]交易所便位于此地<ref>{{Cite web |title=Electronic Finance: Reshaping the Financial Landscape Around the World |url=http://web.worldbank.org/WBSITE/EXTERNAL/TOPICS/EXTENERGY/0,,contentMDK:20708340~pagePK:210058~piPK:210062~theSitePK:336806,00.html |accessdate=2008-09-01 |author=Claessens, Stjin |date=September 2000 |format=PDF |publisher=The World Bank |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080804050013/http://web.worldbank.org/WBSITE/EXTERNAL/TOPICS/EXTENERGY/0,,contentMDK:20708340~pagePK:210058~piPK:210062~theSitePK:336806,00.html |archivedate=2008-08-04 |deadurl=yes}}</ref>。金融服务收入占到了全市市民收入的35%<ref>{{Cite web |title=Challenges Facing the New York Metropolitan Area Economy |url=http://www.newyorkfed.org/research/current_issues/ci12-1.pdf |accessdate=2008-09-01 |author=Orr, James and Giorgio Topa |date=Volume 12, Number 1, January 2006 |format=PDF |work=Current Issues in Economics and Finance – Second District Highlights |publisher=New York Federal Reserve |archive-date=2008-08-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080824013626/http://www.newyorkfed.org/research/current_issues/ci12-1.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>。华尔街[[投资银行|投资银行]]的费用在2012年达到近400亿美元<ref>{{Cite web |title=London Bankers Bracing for Leaner Bonuses Than New York |url=http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-11-27/london-bankers-bracing-for-leaner-bonuses-than-new-york.html |accessdate=2013-02-09 |author=Ambereen Choudhury, Elisa Martinuzzi & Ben Moshinsky |date=2012-11-26 |publisher=Bloomberg L.P. |archive-date=2021-03-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210311000014/http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-11-27/london-bankers-bracing-for-leaner-bonuses-than-new-york.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，而在2013年，在纽约从事[[风险管理|风险管理]]的银行高管年收入能够达到324,000美元<ref>{{Cite web |title=Pay Raises for Bank Risk Officers in Asia Trump New York |url=http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-11-10/pay-raises-for-bank-risk-officers-in-asia-trump-new-york.html |accessdate=2013-11-10 |author=Sanat Vallikappen |date=2013-11-10 |publisher=Bloomberg L.P |archive-date=2020-07-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200714093711/http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-11-10/pay-raises-for-bank-risk-officers-in-asia-trump-new-york.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

曼哈顿金融区有时成为冲突的始发地，例如“[[占领华尔街|占领华尔街]]”及其触发的全球范围内的“[[占领运动|占领运动]]”。有时这类冲突导致了致命的后果，例如1920年的[[华尔街爆炸事件|华尔街爆炸事件]]。

2013年7月，纽约证券交易所的运营商[[纽约泛欧证交所|纽约泛欧证交所]]从{{Link-en|英国银行家协会|British Bankers' Association}}手中接过了[[伦敦同业拆放利率|伦敦同业拆放利率]]的管理权<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://stream.wsj.com/story/the-libor-investigation/SS-2-32262/SS-2-272592/ |title=NYSE Euronext to Take Over Libor |author=David Enrich, Jacob Bunge, and Cassell Bryan-Low |date=2013-07-09 |publisher=The Wall Street Journal |accessdate=2013-07-10 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131019203758/http://stream.wsj.com/story/the-libor-investigation/SS-2-32262/SS-2-272592/ |archivedate=2013-10-19 |dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

== 房地产 ==
房地产是该市经济的主要力量，2017年纽约市房地产总价值估计为1.072万亿美元，比上一年增加10.6％，其中89％的增长来自于市场影响。时代华纳中心在该市最具市场价值，2006年市值为11亿美元。纽约市房地产价值居世界上首位。公园大道450号于2007年7月2日以5.1亿美元的价格售出，均价17,104美元/平方米，打破了美国写字楼均价15,887美元/平方米的纪录。
